This is a android application where you can easily give and take bitcoins as payment.

Description (English)
	This is a android application where you can easily give and take bitcoins as payment.

Recent Changes (English)
	Added support for green address. (thanks to javgh)
	
Promo Text (English)
	Send and receive bitcoins with your smartphone.	

